{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/problems/layout,_N_T_/problems/[slug]/layout,_N_T_/problems/[slug]/page,_N_T_/problems/maximum-profitable-triplets-with-increasing-prices-i"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/problems/$d$slug/__PAGE__","/problems/$d$slug","/problems","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.0r6juujl39pe6.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.0wgildi0cnwt9.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/340fxer6uczx7.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/05kafvajig4wu.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/2o5-igl1ik8oj.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1uejzok0tpgy1.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3ujjz4ap-oopx.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-3om3j4o09b7fr.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/2fvm6eoqeukxu.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1ntn7efqc-iiw.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0plpm2axnqe9k.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/259rkrk9l2f9c.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I Solution — Medium | AlgoForge</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Original Medium explanation for Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I (LeetCode #2907). Pattern: prefix sum. Time O(nlogn), space O(n). Multi-language solutions and interview tips.\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I,Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I solution,Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I leetcode,binary-search-tree,prefix-sum,sorted-list,binary-search,stack,fenwick-tree,segment-tree,medium\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/maximum-profitable-triplets-with-increasing-prices-i\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I Solution — Medium | AlgoForge\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Original Medium explanation for Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I (LeetCode #2907). Pattern: prefix sum. Time O(nlogn), space O(n). Multi-language solutions and interview tips.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/maximum-profitable-triplets-with-increasing-prices-i\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"AlgoForge\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://algoforge.dev/og-default.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I Solution — Medium | AlgoForge\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I Solution — Medium | AlgoForge\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Original Medium explanation for Maximum Profitable Triplets With Increasing Prices I (LeetCode #2907). Pattern: prefix sum. Time O(nlogn), space O(n). Multi-language solutions and interview tips.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://algoforge.dev/og-default.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/><script src=